description:
This is where I buy my coffee.  In a city with a rainbow of hip choices (Philz, Ritual,Blue Bottle) - Beanery is the real deal.  I've spent twice as much for dry, flavorless beans and I always wonder what the fuss is about.  And I love this quote from one reviewer;
" What's the point of a hanging out at a café on a rainy day if it doesn't offer internet access?"  
The point is, you don't have to hang out with plugged in dweebs!
